{"tid":855250,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"（俄妹湯）分享煮羅宋湯","createTime":"2018-10-10T02:49:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T01:05:19.000Z","uid":43964,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"adab53bf50ee93860dc6b82655c41242d81f5295","tid":855250,"uid":43964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:49:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/103956_816e9d2c624921a381a63afe56638597.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F103956_816e9d2c624921a381a63afe56638597.png&h=06a725e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實好易煮！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日材料有 <br />\nPotato x1<br />\nCelery x 2sticks<br />\nCarrot x 1stick<br />\nBeets x 2 <br />\nOnion = half<br />\nCabbage = half<br />\nGarlic x 4 cloves <br />\nChicken breast x2 <br />\nChicken stock 1L<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/104305_0b5cfd3a5c4f087f5d7bc9910663322e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F104305_0b5cfd3a5c4f087f5d7bc9910663322e.png&h=2063abdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住就係考驗你的手同把刀， 材料切成圖中咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/104358_16f4464d70afb23b6282480b67e56444.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F104358_16f4464d70afb23b6282480b67e56444.png&h=a1b89cd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住用個大煲， 炒一炒洋蔥同garlic先，有香味後，落埋其他蔬菜，炒佢10分鐘左右<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/104521_df58bbb10577f4bea2c57a29b5729c4a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F104521_df58bbb10577f4bea2c57a29b5729c4a.png&h=9fd62d6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住落雞湯，上蓋 煲佢9個字左右，咁等佢煮湯既時候，煎雞肉啦<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/104629_b5503048185c5aab697c0916c31cea90.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F104629_b5503048185c5aab697c0916c31cea90.png&h=e14a9488&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n煎完用差差 撕開佢，手撕雞咁<br />\n<br />\n咁9個字後落埋啲雞雞就食得。可以落sour cream 同dill 草碎，但我唔記得買<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後送俄妹圖<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/104847_a21f930f5069168b86ee1e2a2768df9f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F104847_a21f930f5069168b86ee1e2a2768df9f.png&h=ed997071&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/104849_8f45b6a60ad9c4d7224036e10b3f5777.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F104849_8f45b6a60ad9c4d7224036e10b3f5777.png&h=2c2e14f8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/104850_f5d0933fdbdfe43c0acd1e5d5c1dd0f1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F104850_f5d0933fdbdfe43c0acd1e5d5c1dd0f1.png&h=ccc1e2a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/104852_ad55767c6c429ba54be540624f240120.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F104852_ad55767c6c429ba54be540624f240120.png&h=d41b0bc2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/104854_c4b009b7a9cf23283b4140874e38fef8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F104854_c4b009b7a9cf23283b4140874e38fef8.png&h=d1fc8c30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我果個湯仲煮緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a84ee69c3f0ddc7c97619aa724a856db241e1b5","tid":855250,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:59:37.000Z","msg":"俄妹more<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eee01185433e5dd55ba3be2c3faf7953b3c825c","tid":855250,"uid":43964,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:16:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/111536_a52868789d54db8724b4268e88f02659.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F111536_a52868789d54db8724b4268e88f02659.png&h=3e184fa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n煮完，個湯好甜🤔"},{"pid":"822366e17829cb0999526691ddabe709269330c6","tid":855250,"uid":76105,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8eee01185433e5dd55ba3be2c3faf7953b3c825c","tid":855250,"uid":43964,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:16:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/111536_a52868789d54db8724b4268e88f02659.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F111536_a52868789d54db8724b4268e88f02659.png&h=3e184fa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n煮完，個湯好甜🤔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:39:49.000Z","msg":"以為碗仔翅 多醋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b83dbbb89d960d974ebf77be5918ca13197f0e2","tid":855250,"uid":43964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"822366e17829cb0999526691ddabe709269330c6","tid":855250,"uid":76105,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8eee01185433e5dd55ba3be2c3faf7953b3c825c","tid":855250,"uid":43964,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:16:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/111536_a52868789d54db8724b4268e88f02659.png\" data-thumbnail-src